      "text": "You Are The Reviewer\nYour control point is task definition up front and\nreview afterward. Think code review and curation,\nnot keystroke approval.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-ffed504a0ea7",
      "originalText": "You Are The Reviewer\nYour control point is task definition up front and review afterward. Think code review and curation, not keystroke approval.",
