      "text": "Iterate Or Commit\nStay in the same thread when the task needs refinement.\nCommit only after the curated diff is acceptable.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-245e53c34649",
      "originalText": "Iterate Or Commit\nStay in the same thread when the task needs refinement. Commit only after the curated diff is acceptable.",
