      "text": "Stage Selects Commit\nStage means \"include this in the next commit.\" Use it\nwhen you want to keep part or all of the diff.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
